{"tid":1377542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人已經無退路","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:25:10.000Z","uid":2503,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1e459782d3ba9a76ce58d2f6d167bb471792f19f","tid":1377542,"uid":2503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:04:43.000Z","msg":"上次和理非佔中失敗之後，中共同港共已經瘋狂秋後算帳<br />\n今次嘅運動如果又係失敗同不了了之，之後嘅清算會超出所有人嘅想像<br />\n<br />\n中共一定會再加速殖民，大公司(特別中資)同政府中高層會比支那人佔據大部份職位<br />\n大學學額都一樣會支那人侵蝕<br />\n<br />\n香港人已經無退路，一定要繼續堅持抗爭落去<br />\n警犬可以拉幾百，幾千人，但只要每一次抗爭都有人肯企出嚟，佢地可以拉嘅人都係有限"},{"pid":"414cd2fd10d330a9f7c58cae5945ddcb846605ca","tid":1377542,"uid":2503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5b7ae49f0bf3dc918dbdf6e86ecc2c55e0e31f","tid":1377542,"uid":262557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:02:14.000Z","msg":"退一步將會萬劫不復！"},{"pid":"0f54aba088eb0633c35a96ab137068d4d021d2e4","tid":1377542,"uid":229733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T23:03:49.000Z","msg":"人同物資都好重要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自己香港自己救</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[窮學生] 我只需要你地管理好物！資！仲有上！前！線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383889</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"82fa5ce9933b4993b71391f26da2a599fb30d117","tid":1377542,"uid":2503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:14:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcaacec936a87a1c7a432225fb9fbe6ca42c50c6","tid":1377542,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:16:14.000Z","msg":"鬥長命"},{"pid":"ed0898479f3acd20a37cd7a65e2f09a6151985e1","tid":1377542,"uid":2503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fcaacec936a87a1c7a432225fb9fbe6ca42c